author: @park_ramyeon
text:
I have a poem, hope you enjoy it everyone and also NewJeans 🫶🏻:     
In the heart of Seoul, under the neon lights,
A star was born, reaching dazzling heights.
A K-pop idol, with a voice so clear,
Embarking bravely on a career.

She danced and sang, her spirit free,
On stages grand for all to see.
Her music spread, both near and far,
A radiant, rising superstar.

Through sleepless nights and endless days,
She honed her craft in countless ways.
Her melodies, they touched the heart,
Each note a vital, vibrant part.

Her fans, they cheered, their love so deep,
Their faith in her, a pact to keep.
Through highs and lows, through joy and pain,
Her music, their solace and refrain.

Yet fame and fortune, they demand,
A price not all can understand.
The lights, the cheers, the constant show,
Can take a toll, as well we know.

But she, with strength and grace combined,
Kept moving forward, never maligned.
Her dreams, her passion, her unwavering will,
Kept her standing, strong and still.

A K-pop idol, her star shines bright,
In the vast expanse of the music night.
Her journey, a testament to her art,
A melody etched in every heart.
